## Attribution

When reusing processed tables, figures or derived statistics from this
repository, please cite:

> Tani, H. *Grounding RNA foundation models in transcript dynamics.*
> Manuscript submitted. DOI to be updated upon publication.

## Upstream data licenses

Processed tables in `data/processed/` are derived from third-party public
datasets that retain their original licenses and attribution requirements:

| Upstream dataset | Original citation | Accession |
|---|---|---|
| BRIC-seq (HeLa Tet-off) | Tani et al. *Genome Res.* 22, 947-956 (2012) | GSE30792 |
| SLAM-seq (mESC) | Herzog et al. *Nat. Methods* 14, 1198-1204 (2017) | GSE99970 |
| TimeLapse-seq (K562, MEF) | Schofield et al. *Nat. Methods* 15, 221-225 (2018) | GSE103493 |
| GENCODE annotations | Frankish et al. *Nucleic Acids Res.* 51, D942 (2023) | v44 / vM33 |

Users redistributing the processed tables must also comply with the upstream
licenses listed above.
